'''药菓'''（{{lang-ko|약과}}）是一种[[韩国料理|韩国传统食品]]。最初当作[[甜品|甜品]]，但因味甜、带有花的形状，如今多当作[[菓子|菓子]]（[[韩菓|韩菓]]）。药菓主要由[[蜂蜜|蜂蜜]]、[[芝麻油|芝麻油]]和[[小麦粉|小麦粉]]制成。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.doopedia.co.kr/doopedia/master/master.do?_method=view&MAS_IDX=101013000754620|title=약과|publisher=Doopedia|accessdate=2015-05-24|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111225719/https://www.doopedia.co.kr/doopedia/master/master.do?_method=view&MAS_IDX=101013000754620|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://koreanfood.about.com/od/holidaysandoccasions/r/How-to-Make-Yakgwa-a-Korean-Honey-Cookie.htm|title=How to Make Yakgwa, Korean Honey Cookies|publisher=About.com|accessdate=2015-05-24|language=en|archive-date=2015-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150622133215/http://koreanfood.about.com/od/holidaysandoccasions/r/How-to-Make-Yakgwa-a-Korean-Honey-Cookie.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Sweet Treats around the World: An Encyclopedia of Food and Culture|url=https://archive.org/details/sweettreatsaroun0000rouf|publisher=ABC-CLIO|year=2014|author=Timothy G. Roufs, Kathleen Smyth Roufs|isbn=9781610692212|pages=[https://archive.org/details/sweettreatsaroun0000rouf/page/213 213]}}</ref>因這種點心製作時以蜂蜜為主要食材，又因傳統上蜂蜜被認為有健康療效，對身體有益，所以才以藥菓命名。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/102454 |title=韓國傳統點心：藥果 |accessdate=2019-11-15 |archive-date=2019-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191115133616/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/102454 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

